  Locus:
    Page: 241
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Heaven & Hell
---
The “Kingdom of Heaven” is in the heart of those who realize God and the
whole purpose of life is to make God a reality. Verily, it is simpler to
find a way to Heaven than to find one’s way on earth.
